{"tid":1835040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】消委會曾測試29款口罩 3款過濾細菌效率逾99.9%","createTime":"2020-01-22T16:17:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T06:35:20.000Z","uid":65449,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e822e37f26bd37b21fcdec6dd099b2681ed95407","tid":1835040,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:17:19.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎陰霾下，市民又再搶購口罩，但選用口罩要注意細菌過濾效率，否則保護效果大打折扣。消委會於第494期的《選擇》月刊曾就29款市面上的口罩進行測試，對各款口罩作評估，範疇包括細菌過濾效率、顆粒過濾效率、顯示樣本透氣程度的壓力差，及模擬醫護人員進行醫護工序時飛濺血液的合成血穿透測試。<br />\n<br />\n消委會表示，根據美國材料和試驗協會（American Society for Testing and Material， ASTM）F2100-11要求，口罩材料分為3個級別：第一級低防護、第二級中防護及第三級高防護。根據第一級防護指標，其過濾細菌的效率須達95%。<br />\n<br />\n調查結果顯示，有13款樣本表現良好，總評獲最高的5分，11款獲4.5分，但有2款分別僅獲2分和1分。當中3款口罩的細菌過濾效率均高逾99.9%，包括「麥迪康Medicom Safe+」SPSHMK2585彩色生活口罩耳掛式（中國製）、「Elleair超強阻隔PM2.5成人口罩（標準）」（中國製）及「理的Ultra Ready」外科手術口罩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總評獲最低1分的樣本，其細菌過濾效率只有60.4%，即是Disposable Face Mask Two Ply﹔另一款標有「高效細菌過濾」字眼的樣本，也只有88.5%，品牌為加護CANCARE SurgicMask醫用口罩，也都不達標。<br />\n<br />\n因應近日武漢爆發不明原因的肺炎，加上本港亦踏入季流感高峰期，消委會將以上有關口罩選擇月刊報告，供大家免費下載：<a href=\"https://echoice.consumer.org.hk/article/494-4472\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fechoice.consumer.org.hk%2Farticle%2F494-4472&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzADrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=465502c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://echoice.consumer.org.hk/article/494-4472</a><br />\n<br />\n報章來源<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1677066\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1677066&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzADrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=69f6bdf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1677066</a>"},{"pid":"6e3654dc32566f12c733dd4d57988ae7d68f25c3","tid":1835040,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:18:15.000Z","msg":"消委會測試結果<br />\n<a href=\"https://echoice.consumer.org.hk/article/494-4472\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fechoice.consumer.org.hk%2Farticle%2F494-4472&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzADrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=465502c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://echoice.consumer.org.hk/article/494-4472</a>"},{"pid":"6b3581eeb1ff758cc30767d6528d162b787427fd","tid":1835040,"uid":65449,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:20:28.000Z","msg":"推上熱門 等咁多位唔洗買中伏口罩 我就係過來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ede1625f17c54e82e966efa36d1eeed653db07","tid":1835040,"uid":36058,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:21:22.000Z","msg":"過濾細菌有撚用咩，新型肺炎係病毒（virus）引致。"},{"pid":"a75bbdd0ffbfadfea2e3463841142bf5f9f9c833","tid":1835040,"uid":172668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:24:06.000Z","msg":"而家都係唔好買made in china<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce5cc7d8bbfd7f1b27df5010fab0ffef1b66c366","tid":1835040,"uid":36040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b3581eeb1ff758cc30767d6528d162b787427fd","tid":1835040,"uid":65449,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:20:28.000Z","msg":"推上熱門 等咁多位唔洗買中伏口罩 我就係過來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:24:50.000Z","msg":"問題係5星嗰啲都唔知邊度有得買"},{"pid":"bf12109ce9765448ff828a76e083c7f93cad4856","tid":1835040,"uid":65449,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"34ede1625f17c54e82e966efa36d1eeed653db07","tid":1835040,"uid":36058,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:21:22.000Z","msg":"過濾細菌有撚用咩，新型肺炎係病毒（virus）引致。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:26:02.000Z","msg":"吓 我屌呀 佢冇驗喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=